  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.5,
    "endTime": 32.5,
    "text": "Well, time to get to work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.5,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "And for your final question, my friends would describe me as..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 40.5,
    "text": "Smart, funny, kind, or brave?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.5,
    "endTime": 42.5,
    "text": "Um..."
