  {
    "startTime": 42.5,
    "endTime": 44.5,
    "text": "Kind, I guess?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.5,
    "endTime": 48.5,
    "text": "Based on your answers, your princess BFF is..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.5,
    "endTime": 50.5,
    "text": "Snow White!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.5,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "I do believe our friendship would be the fairest of them all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "Hey, hey, hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.0,
    "endTime": 56.5,
    "text": "Want to meet my BFF?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.5,
    "endTime": 57.5,
    "text": "It's Wreck-It-Rob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.5,
    "endTime": 59.5,
    "text": "Be sure to see his new video."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.5,
    "endTime": 61.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.5,
    "endTime": 64.5,
    "text": "Yeah, um, in Captain America, the first Avenger,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.5,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "Red Skull refers to Yggdrasil, the World Tree, guardian of wisdom and faith."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "Are we to believe, sir, that you are a descendant of that tree?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 74.5,
    "text": "I am Groot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.5,
    "endTime": 77.0,
    "text": "Okay, okay, thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 79.5,
    "text": "Um, what is Drax really like?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.5,
    "endTime": 80.5,
    "text": "I am Groot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.5,
    "endTime": 81.5,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.5,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Yeah, are you a conifer or a fruit-bearing tree?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 85.5,
    "text": "Excuse me, I'll take this one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.5,
    "endTime": 86.5,
    "text": "He is Groot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.5,
    "endTime": 87.5,
    "text": "I am Vanellope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.5,
    "endTime": 89.5,
    "text": "Click here to meet Wreck-It-Rob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.5,
    "endTime": 92.5,
    "text": "This is almost too easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 95.5,
    "text": "Hey, you have a permit for that pop-up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.5,
    "endTime": 97.5,
    "text": "That's unauthorized clickbait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.5,
    "endTime": 99.5,
    "text": "You're coming with us, kid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.5,
    "endTime": 101.5,
    "text": "She's getting away!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.5,
    "endTime": 105.5,
    "text": "This way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.5,
    "endTime": 108.5,
    "text": "Sorry, mister!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.5,
    "endTime": 113.5,
    "text": "Hey, can't you read?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.5,
    "endTime": 114.5,
    "text": "Memories only!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.5,
    "endTime": 117.5,
    "text": "I think she went down this way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.5,
    "endTime": 118.5,
    "text": "Come on, roger that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.5,
    "endTime": 120.5,
    "text": "Did you see a kid come through here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.5,
    "endTime": 123.5,
    "text": "Came running through here like a headless man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.5,
    "endTime": 126.5,
    "text": "Any sign of her?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.5,
    "endTime": 127.5,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.5,
    "endTime": 129.5,
    "text": "Maybe she went down to the Earbud Pavilion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.5,
    "endTime": 131.5,
